title.value: Cross-version Extension for R5.ServiceRequest.orderDetail for use in FHIR R4

description.value: This cross-version extension represents ServiceRequest.orderDetail from http://hl7.org/fhir/StructureDefinition/ServiceRequest|5.0.0 for use in FHIR R4.

definition.value: Additional details and instructions about the how the services are to be delivered.
